Cassandra Cassidy was fatally wounded in a drive-by shooting outside a rehab centre in Las Vegas on Friday night . 
  She had been stopped by two women 'afraid of men in a car' outside the centre . 
  The fashion design student was shot as she was talking to the women and died in hospital . 
  Ms Cassidy worked at a half-way house for people struggling with substance abuse . 
  The women approached her outside the rehab centre and said they were afraid of the men in the car . 
  She was shot by a car as she tried to help the women but survived . 
 